I’m speechless, in tears, and shaking as I type this. 
First off, a HUGE SHOUTOUT to @mintmediasocial and @keepitmovinfilms for capturing a HUGE milestone for me. I was NOT expecting this at all. You guys work magic, and I can see why you are the BEST in the game. Thank you for understanding how important this was to me and for delivering beyond my expectations!! This is memorable. 

To see my niece play my role in the flashback scene is EVERYTHING. She was also born and raised in this exceptional home. I can’t even explain how special this is to me. 

Many of you have been asking about the makeover, and being honest, I can’t even wrap my head around how my brother @sinshan21 managed to transform our old home into this STUNNING WORK OF ART. This is PURE TALENT and dedication. He hand-picked everything you see in this house and brought his vision to reality. The demand he has been getting from this one project is overwhelming! Passion does outshine everything.

Can we take a moment to appreciate the staging done by @serenestagingco ! You can tell by their work; they’re PERFECTIONISTS! 

Thank you, @pavetheway.to, for sealing our driveway and accommodating our schedule! 

A moment of silence for this BOSS WHIP!🚙🔥🔥Thank you, @shapesk, for trusting me with this BEAST. 🙏🏽

Thank you, @luxemediadesigns, for not only designing my logo but also designing my signs! You’ll always be my go-to! 

Thank you, @krishnaprinting, for always accommodating my crazy schedule and printing my signs.

🍒These cherries are called “Rainier Cherries”.
They’re far more sweeter than the normal cherries because they have a low acidity and higher sugar content. They have a crisp bite and delicate, yellow flesh.🤤

Here are the benefits of “Rainier Cherries”:👇🏼
🧡Sunshine for Your Skin Packed with vitamin C + antioxidants to glow from the inside out. ✨
🧡Sweet & Low-Cal Naturally candy-like flavor with zero guilt—perfect healthy snack. 🍬
🧡Anti-Inflammatory Power Fights bloat & aches (anthocyanins FTW!). 💪
🧡Happy Heart Potassium + fiber to support cardiovascular health. ❤️
🧡Hydration Queen Juicy AF—helps you stay refreshed on hot days. 💦
🔅Their golden-red hue = more antioxidants than regular cherries! 🌈

latestPosts.caption:
⚠️ Did you know this notorious fruit is BANNED in some hotels, flights, and public transportation in some countries and regions of Southeast Asia?!😷⛔️ 

But did you also know Durians are THE KING OF FRUITS?!😍👑 (also my FAV fruit ever! —my dad introduced this to me as a child and immediately fell in love with the taste. We shared a mutual passion for trying new fruits❤️🤝🏽)

This specific durian is called “Musang King”👑 
Durians are so accessible and affordable in Southeast Asia! I had 2 durians everyday while I was in Thailand and Malaysia🤤

Durian benefits:👇🏼
👑 Rich in Nutrients – Packed with fiber, vitamins C and B, potassium, and healthy fats.
👑 Boosts Energy – High in carbs and calories, making it a great natural energy source.
👑 Supports Heart Health – Potassium helps regulate blood pressure and improve circulation.
👑 Aids Digestion – Fiber promotes gut health and prevents constipation.
👑 Strengthens Immunity – Loaded with antioxidants and vitamin C to fight infections.
👑 Enhances Mood – Contains tryptophan, which helps produce serotonin, the “feel-good” hormone
👑 Good for Skin – Vitamin C and antioxidants promote collagen production and fight aging.
👑 Improves Bone Health – Rich in magnesium and potassium, essential for strong bones.
